data.description: Welcome to this charming 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home with a desirable bonus room above the garage!! This home offers a split floor plan with covered front and back porches. The spacious kitchen offers elegant granite, a beautiful backsplash, and SS appliances. It opens to the living room with hardwood flooring and a cozy gas fireplace. The hardwood flows into the primary bedroom and hallways. Located just outside the city limits, this property offers the best of both worlds – a peaceful neighborhood while still being close to the amenities and conveniences of the city. With an excellent level lot, this home provides ample space for outdoor activities, gardening, or even the addition of a pool or workshop. Enjoy the firepit! NO HOA! NO City taxes!
